    <p>
        R/L through explaination: You are facing your partner, give right hands to them. Pull by, and drop hands with them. You should see your neighbour that just swung
        coming with you. Give left hands to them, and courtousy turn them, rotating in an anti-clockwise direction. 
    </p>
